. email: Stores the user's email,which must be unique and required. includes a basic regex
 foremail format validation.

. password: Store the hashed password.Required.
. role: Defines the user's role .it's an enum that can only be one of the specified values('regular','accountant','admin'). Defaults to 'regular'.
. createdat: Automatically records the timestamp when the user was created.
. 